{"tid":2434904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"極限跑山｜80後破紀錄連續50小時跑完香港四大山徑共298公里：跑到有幻覺山上聽到歡呼聲","createTime":"2021-03-05T22:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T05:18:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef45ce2ee23d259ba495571d7889d2bcbcbda0b","tid":2434904,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:41:02.000Z","msg":"「我媽會說：『跑跑跑，跑斷腳啦你』；我太太會投訴：『喂，留多一點時間回來吃飯，陪陪兩個女兒』；但我很喜歡那種強迫自己到很累的狀態，要透過suffering（受苦） 或是struggling（掙扎）才找到身體中的潛質。」38歲的梁俊強（Jacky）興奮說道。<br />\n<br />\n麥理浩徑（100km）、衛奕信徑（78km）、港島徑（50km）、鳳凰徑（70km），被稱為香港四大山徑，一般人跑完其中一條，已經要了他們半條人命。但一名旅居香港的德國越野跑高手Andre Blumberg， 每年農曆大年初一都會發起一個名為「香港四大山徑超級挑戰」的極限山跑，廣發「英雄帖」邀請世界各地的跑山高手參加這個總共298公里，垂直上落14,500米的極限山跑比賽。雖然既沒獎金又沒獎牌，但不乏各國高手慕名參加，Jacky就是史上首位在50小時內完成四徑挑戰的跑手，打破2017年由英國跑手創下的53小時紀錄。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210306/I2T5ZODFXNE4BCBV37IYUAG6CE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210306%2FI2T5ZODFXNE4BCBV37IYUAG6CE%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=291b33e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210306%2FI2T5ZODFXNE4BCBV37IYUAG6CE%2F&h=caa3bd70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210306/I2T5ZODFXNE4BCBV37IYUAG6CE/</a>"},{"pid":"d022c96fd35f0932d0cfd68d7df403caaec9f869","tid":2434904,"uid":72306,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:40:13.000Z","msg":"仲講80後，80後都係阿叔黎架啦"},{"pid":"a9f2421162c46e7004eb6e057f77240598369c95","tid":2434904,"uid":99962,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:06:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"},{"pid":"a3184707d5eaf80c27a734f00844dc74fb93e564","tid":2434904,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"跑山路都得咁哩班人跑馬拉松咪好撚easy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93519ff981fd55f9d875da43907ecaaea